overview: The future. Jackson (Gerald Maliqi), an embittered Time Agent, uncovers a 120-year-old mystery. His investigation leads him to the story of Amber (Eve Pemberton), a 21st-century bartender who's just deleted her boyfriend from time. Can Jackson find relevance in these past events and untangle a huge conspiracy? Or is too big for one man alone?
title: Timespiracy
